title: FULLY Furnished Travis Heights BUNGALOW__Dramatic & UNIQUE
posting_body: Located in the heart of Travis heights, 2003 Kenwood was designed by DSLV Studios, and welcomes you with interiors that create a warm and inviting vibe with unexpected details
Built in 1941 with a clean and well-planned floor plan, there is plenty of whimsy and nuance in this 2 bedroom, 1 bath home
The house is surrounded by original glass windows, allowing natural light to pour in
Restored vanity and fixtures give the bathroom a vintage and modern look, while the fabulously updated kitchen features marble countertops and backsplash with stainless steel-clad appliances

Additional features include new sprinkler irrigation system front and back, new Lutron light system with remote functionality, and countless other upgrades, while still maintaining the original bungalow vibe

Enjoy being blocks from Big Stacy Pool and bustling South Congress, or stay in and relax in the expansive backyard - complete with outdoor deck perfect for al fresco dining and a backyard fire pit to relax near later this year.
* I’m Clayton Holsey, a full-time Realtor with Austin Real Pros.
This home is real and so am I!
